trainers.roster: Chandelure-3, Excadrill-4, Haxorus-4
trainers.species: Chandelure, Excadrill, Haxorus
trainers.quote: Welcome! I've been waiting for you! Let me introduce myself... I am the Subway Boss Ingo. What can I see after winning, winning, and winning? Where is my destination? I've kept thinking, and I've learned one thing. That is, you cannot know what happens after winning without winning. Therefore, I will exert every possible effort to battle with you. All aboard!

trainers.name: Emmet
trainers.roster: Eelektross-1, Chandelure-3, Excadrill-4, Haxorus-4
trainers.species: Eelektross, Chandelure, Excadrill, Haxorus
trainers.quote: Hi, do you remember me? I am Emmet. I am a Subway Boss. I like Double Battles. I like combinations of two Pokémon. And I like winning more than anything else. This time, I am really serious. Really serious. Because if a battle is not serious, it is not fun.
